channel.title: Ever wanted to download a liveset?
channel.description:
The [url=http://lsdb.eu/]Liveset Database[/url] now lets you do so!
just search for the liveset you want,
e.g. Eddie Halliwell and it will list all live sets and links to download, its brilliant!
